nd worst of all he can't complain<br />In theory his job is plain&nbsp; (twice)<br /><br /><b>Chorus</b><br />Build something sturdy and beautiful and useful<br />He's always short in one goal<br />He juggles true with elegant and useful<br />and he keeps dropping one ball<br /><br /><b>Verse 2</b><br />His buddies like him alright<br />except they love to criticize<br />They go and take his stuff apart<br />with clever words with clever eyes<br /><br /><b>Verse 3</b><br />Some nights a girl comes to his shop<br />to sip his tea learn something raw<br />his foggy mind his tangled soul<br />want her to stay but let her go</blockquote><div class=\"feedflare\">
