 open lounge</div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IE8XB9UgyVA/Uhgl3OoVQoI/AAAAAAAAAv8/eQbAxzlYPrA/s1600/more-lounge.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-IE8XB9UgyVA/Uhgl3OoVQoI/AAAAAAAAAv8/eQbAxzlYPrA/s320/more-lounge.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">Comfy chairs in front of a whiteboard</div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ki--68j9l6w/UhgmDoVVpeI/AAAAAAAAAwE/v7Fi4kwxN5Q/s1600/lounge-close.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ki--68j9l6w/UhgmDoVVpeI/AAAAAAAAAwE/v7Fi4kwxN5Q/s320/lounge-close.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">even more chairs and more whiteboards</div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zcUJnwLRoHU/UhgmN3XZ5qI/AAAAAAAAAwM/xLmxWCC22zk/s1600/coffee-machine.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-zcUJnwLRoHU/UhgmN3XZ5qI/AAAAAAAAAwM/xLmxWCC22zk/s320/coffee-machine.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: cente